Use the standard library
This is how to prime_fib of n:
  Remember that count is 0
  Remember that a is 2
  Do this 100000 times:
    Remember that is_prime is yes
    Remember that d is 2
    Do this a times:
      When d is less than a, then:
        When remainder of a and d is 0, then:
          Remember that is_prime is no
          Leave the loop
        End when
        Increase d by 1
      But, if not:
        Leave the loop
      End when
    End do
    When is_prime is yes, then:
      Increase count by 1
      When count is n, then:
        The answer is a
      End when
    End when
    Increase a by 1
  End do
